data.description: Seller offering $5000 towards closing costs! Welcome to 529 Wickham Drive in The Summit at Horse Creek.  This home has been immaculately maintained and offers a great open/split floor plan.   Brand new roof!  Has a flex room that could be a 5th bedroom, office or hobby room! Very spacious owner's suite and bathroom.  Beautiful hardwoods in dining and living area. Offers a great outdoor space with covered cabana perfect for relaxing and doing your outdoor cooking. Also has an outdoor building that will convey. Location is very convenient to Aiken and Augusta!  Make your appointment to tour today before it's too late!
